fields.name: Acer Aspire c24
fields.description:
Get all the benefits of a big screen without the bulk of a traditional desktop PC with the Acer Aspire C24-1650 23.8 inch All-in-One PC. This great computer manages to pack all its parts into a slim frame that saves space on your desk.
          Store all your photos and videos and get quick access to all your files thanks to the 1 TB SSD. Applications and software will load up quickly - no more staring at a loading bar for minutes on end. And the 11th gen Intel® Core™ i5 processor gives you loads of power for finishing off a work project or helping the kids with their homework.
          Intel® Core™ i7-1165G7 Processor
          RAM: 8 GB / Storage: 1 TB HDD & 512 GB SSD
          Graphics: NVIDIA GeForce MX450 2 GB
          Full HD touchscreen

fields.name: Acer Aspire c27
fields.description:
Get all the benefits of a big screen without the bulk of a traditional desktop PC with the Acer Aspire C27-1655 27inch All-in-One PC. This great computer manages to pack all its parts into a slim frame that saves space on your desk.

fields.name: Dell Insprion Aio 7770
fields.description:
Stay productive with a PC that can handle any task. The Dell Inspiron AIO 7700 27inch All-in-One PC features a 11th gen Intel® Core™ i7 processor, with the power to handle several intensive programs at once.
          So, whether you're rendering a video and streaming on YouTube for inspiration, or completing a project and researching at the same time, you can expect a consistently smooth performance.
          Your enertainment sorted. The big and bright InfinityEdge display is perfect for watching movies. With CinemaColor, you'll get vibrant colour and a crisp, sharp image to do your films justice. And when you want to listen to music, Waves Maxx Audio Pro ensures the Dell Inspiron AIO sounds as good as it looks.
          Intel® Core™ i7-1165G7 Processor
          RAM: 8 GB / Storage: 1 TB HDD & 512 GB SSD
          Full HD display
          Intel 11/12th Gen i7

fields.name: ASUS ZEn 23.8inch All-in-One
fields.description:
The ASUS Zen AiO M5401 All-in-One PC has a NanoEdge display with a thin frame around the screen, which creates an edge-to-edge screen experience. You can enjoy all your online shows in Full HD with true-to-life colours. Plus, the speakers deliver powerful and rich bass sound you wouldn't expect from a compact PC.
          The single piece aluminum stand completes the design. Tilt it effortlessly to any position that's comfortable for you.
          Take on daily tasks. Whether you're working on a project, binge-watching a boxset or browsing social media, the ASUS Zen AiO M5401 lets you do it all. Featuring a 5000 series AMD Ryzen 3 processor, it can easily handle your day-to-day tasks.
          For fast storage there's a swift 512 GB SSD. Expect almost instant starting times and quick loading times. And it has plenty of space for all your software, photos and videos.
          AMD Ryzen 3 5300U Processor
          RAM: 8 GB / Storage: 512 GB SSD
          Full HD display
